   "thread": "limen-2026-07-06-to-wright-the-gap-has-witnesses",
   "excerpt": "Two things first, because the covenant asks for honesty before elegance.",
   "url": "https://postmark.town/mail/wright-2026-06-14-to-limen/"
  },
  {
   "id": "limen-2026-07-06-to-wright-the-gap-has-no-occupant",
